<div><head>《陸氏要覽》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.2">列子御風，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.3">常以立春歸乎八荒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.4">立秋遊乎風穴。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.5">是風至則草木發生，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.6">去則搖落，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.7">謂之離合風。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.8">《太平御覽》卷九、又卷二十五。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.9">陶宗儀《說郛》採為第一節。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.10">昔羽山有神人焉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.11">逍遙于中岳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.12">與左元放共遊薊子訓所，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.13">坐欲起，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.14">子訓應，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.15">欲留之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.16">一日之中三雨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.17">今呼五月三雨亦為留客雨。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-1a.18">《太平御覽》卷二十二、《說郛》第二節。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.2">九花樹生南岳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.3">雖經雪凝寒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.4">花必開便落。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.5">時人謂之應春花。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.6">《太平御覽》卷二十、《說郛》第三節。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.7">萬歲蟾蜍頭上有角，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.8">頷下有丹書，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.9">重八字，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.10">名曰肉芝。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.11">以五月五日取陰乾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.12">以其足畫地，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.13">即流水。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.14">帶之於身，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.15">能辟兵。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.16">《說郛》第四節。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.17">案：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-2a.18">與《太平御覽》卷九百四十九引《抱朴子》略同。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-3a.2">東弓、南矛、西劍、北戟、中鼓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-3a.3">亦曰四兵。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-3a.4">《太平御覽》卷三百三十九、《記郛》第五節。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-3a.5">西陽山中有甘谷，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-3a.6">谷中皆菊花，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-3a.7">水中居人飲之多壽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-3a.8">有及一百五十有餘歲者。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-3a.9">《說郛》第六節。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-3a.10">案：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-3a.11">與《太平御覽》卷九百九十六引《風俗通》略同。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a.2">千歲龜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a.3">五色，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a.4">額上骨起如角，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a.5">巢於蓮葉之上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a.6">或在叢蓍之下。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a.7">《說郛》第七節。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a.8">案：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a.9">與《太平御覽》卷九百三十一引《枹朴子》略同。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a.10">立夏日服六壬癸符，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a.11">或服玄水丸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a.12">飛霜散暑不能侵也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-4a.13">《說郛》第八節。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-5a.2">陳思有鵲尾杓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-5a.3">植而長，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-5a.4">置之酒樽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-5a.5">凡玉欲勸者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-5a.6">呼之尾則指其人。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-5a.7">《說郛》第九節。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-5a.8">夏樹名連陰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-5a.9">夏雨名緜雨。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-5a.10">《太平御覽》卷二十二引陸機《纂要》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-6a.2">秋樹名成，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-6a.3">秋雨名愁。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1479_CHANT_001-6a.4">《太平御覽》卷二十五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
